# Phase 15: Restoring Sidebar Navigation Logic

The user reported confusion because the "Download" sidebar item was incorrectly leading to the activity manager instead of the version selection list. This phase restores the correct user flow.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Navigation Mapping Restoration
#### [MODIFY] [MainWindow.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/MainWindow.xaml.cs)
- Revert the [NavigateToPage](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/MainWindow.xaml.cs#125-151) tag for `download` to point to `Views.DownloadPage`.
- Move the [DownloadManagerPage](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/DownloadManagerPage.xaml.cs#11-16) navigation to be accessible only via the floating activity button (already implemented in [DownloadManagerPanel.xaml.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/DownloadManagerPanel.xaml.cs)).

### 2. UI Aesthetic Alignment (Optional/Polish)
#### [MODIFY] [DownloadPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/DownloadPage.xaml)
- Ensure the [DownloadPage](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/DownloadPage.xaml.cs#7-11) background matches the `iOS26.Background` for consistency.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Click "Download" in the sidebar: Should show "下载新版本" list.
- Click the floating "View Progress" button (when a download is active): Should show "管理活动下载" page.
- Ensure transitions between these pages are smooth.
